{"tid":953310,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同異性朋友同床瞓，求攻略","createTime":"2018-12-24T00:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T03:27:43.000Z","uid":87765,"like":4,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"85c6cde78d81f066655056957c8028a48eceaf42","tid":953310,"uid":87765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:07:18.000Z","msg":"Exchange個時識左個讀Maste既台灣女仔，26歲到，黎緊會一齊去一個禮拜旅行<br />\n<br />\nBook 房既時候我話想book雙人房慳錢，佢爽快咁話ok<br />\n<br />\n咁聽日平安夜，小弟唔想個小弟咁寂寞，希望幫佢搵個妹妹做玩伴<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法可以令我地打破友誼既隔膜，用啪啪聲迎接聖誕呢？<br />\n<br />\n飲酒，玩game?<br />\n<br />\n又有咩signal表示佢同意搞？<br />\n<br />\n如果成事，定必奉上賽後報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位聖誕快樂"},{"pid":"2d5f4ac86eb8e6360a1d8e409d2ef9473e1b6ce4","tid":953310,"uid":46835,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:08:14.000Z","msg":"賤格"},{"pid":"08ac3177a2c61eced25b5c8391f09cfc4d7f4618","tid":953310,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:09:05.000Z","msg":"賤格"},{"pid":"06ae6d32982f8bca1b88e711b7b0998d32a05b79","tid":953310,"uid":33843,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:09:27.000Z","msg":"同床訓嗰時 近佢方向隻手摸佢背脊"},{"pid":"fa7c66aac78a3f3e8000385be5c8709c0e5be150","tid":953310,"uid":33391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:09:57.000Z","msg":"唔係鐘意人就咪食人隻豬啦"},{"pid":"ce039792f1e10394fcc44e5f01a46432d639aa33","tid":953310,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:10:19.000Z","msg":"賤格"},{"pid":"80aa88d68ba7a95187ec225312395a010415c81b","tid":953310,"uid":146376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:11:00.000Z","msg":"台灣女仔？直接上馬"},{"pid":"99c94aad49e1156887fc6a67fc27465f2cd5bec9","tid":953310,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:11:08.000Z","msg":"賤格"},{"pid":"36bd9a10243cdfbda6191598cef1f49e8d4e0830","tid":953310,"uid":173326,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:11:34.000Z","msg":"台灣人滿腦子都係搞野，一定狼過你，所以只需要準備安全措施"},{"pid":"6aff973305392e3bf2fbc855cad9d467662fac12","tid":953310,"uid":87765,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"2d5f4ac86eb8e6360a1d8e409d2ef9473e1b6ce4","tid":953310,"uid":46835,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:08:14.000Z","msg":"賤格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:15:33.000Z","msg":"若果你情我願，無感情基礎，有咩問題？"},{"pid":"a4cf1da76aafdbeb06751736702352491704920f","tid":953310,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:20:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5df7b349cad928ad71d031929928f5ea70a76c4b","tid":953310,"uid":43842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:24:01.000Z","msg":"記得係閉路面前互錫"},{"pid":"bb7dadc95c5d973a51a0afa8a38b78e0f29e73c4","tid":953310,"uid":98474,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:24:20.000Z","msg":"所以咪話，台灣真係一個充滿住bitch同厹既地方，呢個地方既人成個腦除左諗點樣恥笑香港叫支那之外<br />\n就係諗住做愛，sex，做愛，外遇，偷情，同人妻人夫做愛，亂倫， 強姦，迷姦，撿屍<br />\n一有時間就諗下可以點樣屌到自己個呀嫂，堂/表姐妹，女朋友/老婆嘅姊妹，或者朋友個女，朋友個孫，弱智信徒嘅弱智女、 弱智孫女，老闆屌女秘書，醫生屌女病人，偷嘢女客人主動叫處男店員屌佢同幫佢口交<br />\n老師就想同自己個學生做下愛咁，學生又諗下點屌個大波miss<br />\n再唔係就係最鍾意做愛果時拍下片，方便以後分手再要脅下個前度做多幾次分手愛<br />\n台妹最馨同條仔吵兩句嘴就馬上搵前度傾心事，傾傾下就又做愛<br />\n個前度問佢可唔可以內射，台妹搖頭說不，但最後還是被射滿滿<br />\n所以話，呢個地方真係十分淫亂"},{"pid":"448825785e0958a43420f41baaa21088c29ba9a7","tid":953310,"uid":79605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:31:42.000Z","msg":"試下入佢中路"},{"pid":"86d99e39a0a3607585b5100f4861c49af2abbbe4","tid":953310,"uid":134864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:33:11.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"cdf914bdc05444f6cf2799c4c1306d380c0f7872","tid":953310,"uid":117281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T00:34:16.000Z","msg":"賤格"},{"pid":"ff40c36dde5b4bd31befdac39b7d9b64ec6f1219","tid":953310,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":